These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-1::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: satire, scientific, superhero, musical
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, may, september, january
There are 4 different favourite colors: fuchsia, blue, ivory, green
4 different pets are kept: cat, fish, frog, rabbit
1. the person who's birthday is in may is the person watching satire movies##1
2. the person who likes green is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
3. the person who likes ivory is the person who's birthday is in february##1
4. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
5. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
6. the person who likes fuchsia is on the left of the person who likes blue##1
7. the person who's birthday is in may is the owner of the cat##1
8. the person who likes blue is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
9. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the owner of the frog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Movie-Genre         | satire  | musical  | scientific | superhero |
| Birthday           | may | february | january  | september  |
| Color   | green       | ivory      | fuchsia | blue      |
| Pet           | cat          | fish     | frog    | rabbit     |

