.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, iced-tea, sprite, tea
City: berlin, venice, boston, new-york
There are 4 different nationalities: indonesian, turkish, polish, argentine
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, ritmeester, siglo, prince
1. the person traveling to berlin is on the far right##1
2. the argentine is the tiparillo-smoker##1
3. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
4. the siglo-smoker is on the left of the person traveling to venice##1
5. the argentine is on the left of the indonesian##1
6. the person drinking sprite is the polish##1
7. the turkish is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
8. the siglo-smoker is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
9. the tiparillo-smoker is on the right of the prince-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Beverage      | sprite     | cola       | iced-tea | tea        |
| City          | new-york     | venice       | boston   | berlin   |
| Nationality   | polish      | turkish       | argentine     | indonesian    |
| Cigar         | siglo | prince | tiparillo | ritmeester |

