.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, hot-chocolate, mirinda, tea
There 4 different types of food: artichoke, cranberry, cherry, pineapple
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daisy, amaryllis, dahlia, tulip
House: cottage, palace, gothic-revival, colonial
 1. the person drinking tea is the colonial house##1
 2. the person drinking mirinda is on the far right##1
 3. the person who growsdahlia is on the far right##1
 4. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the cottage house##1
 5. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person who growsdaisy##1
 6. the person who growsdaisy is on the left of the person who growsamaryllis##1
 7. the person who growsamaryllis is on the right of the person eating cranberry##1
 8. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person eating artichoke##1
 9. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the colonial house##1
10. the person drinking mirinda is the person eating pineapple##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3      |       4        |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | 7up       | tea        | mirinda        |
| Food           | cranberry   | cherry | artichoke   | pineapple |
| Flower   | daisy     | amaryllis    | tulip | dahlia        |
| House           | gothic-revival         | cottage  | colonial       | palace         |

