.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-4::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daisy, sunflower, bellflower, zinnia
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: august, september, november, december
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, dutch, thai, turkish
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, coffee, water, soy-milk
1. the thai is on the left of the person who growsdaisy##1
2. the person who growsbellflower is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
3. the person who's birthday is in august is on the far right##1
4. the person who growszinnia is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
5. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
6. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person who growssunflower##1
7. the person who growszinnia is on the right of the person who growsdaisy##1
8. the australian is on the far right##1
9. the person drinking water is the turkish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |      4      |
| Flower           | sunflower   | daisy  | zinnia | bellflower |
| Birthday   | november | december       | september       | august     |
| Nationality   | thai       | turkish    | dutch     | australian  |
| Beverage           | coffee     | water | soy-milk     | almond-milk         |

