.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-5::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  analyst, social-worker, teacher, videographer
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: indie, metal, hip-hop, pop
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, fonseca, dunhill, bluemaster
The people have 4 different hobbies: puzzles, chess, singing, camping
1. the fan of hip-hop is on the far left##1
2. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the analyst##1
3. the person who's hobby is chess is on the far left##1
4. the fonseca-smoker is on the left of the bolivar-smoker##1
5. the bluemaster-smoker is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
6. the person who's hobby is camping is the dunhill-smoker##1
7. the bolivar-smoker is on the left of the fan of indie##1
8. the social-worker is on the right of the fan of metal##1
9. the fan of indie is on the right of the teacher##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |       3       |      4       |
| Job           | analyst  | teacher    | social-worker | videographer |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop      | metal    | indie         | pop    |
| Cigar   | fonseca   | bolivar     | dunhill          | bluemaster      |
| Hobby         | chess | puzzles | camping      | singing      |

