.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-6::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skiing, cycling, water-polo, cricket
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, november, january, august
There are 4 different favourite colors: light-blue, brown, emerald, yellow
4 different pets are kept: fish, frog, horse, mouse
 1. the person who's sport is water-polo is the person who likes light-blue##1
 2. the person who's sport is skiing is the person who likes brown##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in june is the person who likes light-blue##1
 4. the owner of the horse is the person who's sport is skiing##1
 5. the person who likes emerald is the person who's birthday is in august##1
 6. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
 8. the person who likes light-blue is on the right of the person who likes emerald##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in january is on the far left##1
10. the owner of the fish is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |     3      |     4     |
| Sport          | skiing  | cricket | water-polo     | cycling |
| Birthday           | january  | august      | june | november    |
| Color   | brown | emerald  | light-blue    | yellow  |
| Pet           | horse   | mouse       | fish       | frog      |

