4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bluemaster, alhambra, aristoff, vegafina
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: sunflower, balloon-flower, rose, amaryllis
 1. the bluemaster-smoker is the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 2. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the person eating garlic##1
 3. the person eating pineapple is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 4. the alhambra-smoker is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 5. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the vegafina-smoker##1
 6. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
 7. the bluemaster-smoker is the person who growsrose##1
 8. the person eating lemon is on the far left##1
 9. the person eating lemon is on the left of the person eating garlic##1
10. the person who growssunflower is on the left of the person who growsrose##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Food    | lemon | garlic     | pineapple    | pomegranate |
| Hobby       | baking | sudoku    | woodworking | cooking |
| Cigar         | alhambra   | aristoff  | vegafina        | bluemaster    |
