3. the tower house is on the far left##1
4. the palace house is the person driving the scooter##1
5. the craftsman house is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
6. the person driving the train is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
7. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person driving the car##1
8. the person driving the train is the craftsman house##1
9. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |    3     |      4      |
| House      | tower     | craftsman           | ranch-style    | palace    |
| Transport         | airplane  | train | car  | scooter |
| Birthday   | july     | december     | september | october   |
