 7. the colombian is on the far right##1
 8. the owner of the fish is the person watching western movies##1
 9. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
10. the person watching epic movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |      2       |        3        |      4      |
